\'a0\'a0-- The user can specify an object type to add to the Structure. \'a0It will default to Requirement, but persist any change to the selection \'a0\
\'a0\'a0-- The user can type a Short Description for the new object and click the OK button.  \
\'a0\'a0-- The user can also type a Short Description for the new object and click Enter on their keyboard, which will add it to the structure\
\'a0\'a0-- After adding the New object, the focus will be returned to the Short Description input field so that the user can immediately type-add another object\
  -- Users can close the dialog by clicking on the close action\
