\b \cf0 Organizing Nodes in the structure
\b0 \
- To change the order of the structure, the user can select one or more nodes and drag them to a new location in the structure \'a0\
- To add nodes to a parent, the user can drop the selected nodes on the target parent\
- Dragging will include visual indicators to indicate the drop location of above, below, or on another node in the structure\
\
\

\b Removing / Deleting Structure Nodes
\b0 \
- When a node(s) has focus, the user can click on the remove action to remove it/them from the structure \'a0\
- When a node(s) has focus, the user can use the keyboard Delete key to remove it/them from the structure\
